## Project

App: **Ngày Lành Tháng Tốt** (ngaytot / ngaylanhthangtot.vn)  
Stack: React Router v7 (Vite) · Supabase (DB + Auth + RLS + Edge Functions) · Vercel · Tailwind CSS · Figma Make (source UI in `src/make-import/`)

## Architecture summary

- **Frontend:** React SPA on Vercel. Pre-render **`/`** for SEO (northstar §7b). Authenticated app routes under **`/app/*`** (align URL strategy during Foundation — Make today uses `/`, `/chon-ngay`, etc.; normalize to RAD guard pattern in plan).
- **Backend:** Supabase only. Client via publishable key + JWT; **RLS** is the auth boundary.
- **Server logic:** Edge Functions — **Bát Tự** proxy (`BAT_TU_*` secrets), **PayOS** checkout + webhook, share resolve/OG, optional cron push. No PayOS or Bát Tự calls from the browser.
- **Design:** Port Make TSX → `app/` routes; keep layout, Tailwind, **motion** dopamine moments; swap mocks for Supabase + `invoke('bat-tu')`.

## What this app does

Vietnamese B2C PWA: pick auspicious dates (**chọn ngày**) and related insights using **Bát Tự Tứ Trụ**, **personalized by saved lá số**. **Credits + PayOS** (bundles/packs, no auto-renew). Anonymous users get **hôm nay** + **tuần này** free. Tone: calm, specific, Vietnamese — see `copy-rules.mdc` + EDS.

## Not building (out of scope)

From northstar §8 / tech-spec §17: generative chatbot; raw almanac tables as primary UI; marketplace thầy; community/UGC; AI-personalized push; non-Vi locale; admin dashboard (use Supabase + PayOS portals); credit gifting; full query history v1; offline engine; auto-recurring subscriptions; self-serve birth-data edit; **multi-person stored “family profiles”** (v1 = session-only others per shortcut).

## LLM rules

**No LLM features.** Deterministic engine + templates only (tech-spec §13–14 omitted).

## AI module boundary

N/A — no AI SDK in app or Edge for generative UX.

## Key constraints

- **Auth (northstar §9):** Google OAuth + email/password; **anonymous** browse for free calendar/teaser — not Phone OTP (ignore northstar W1 table typo).
- **PayOS only** — no Stripe unless product changes.
- **Feature credit keys:** DB canonical names in `feature_credit_costs`; map Make mocks (`la_so` → `tu_tru`, etc.) — see tech-spec §4.
- **PayOS `package_sku`:** `le`, `goi_6thang`, `goi_12thang` only.
- **`scripts`/screen-specs:** Phase 2 file not generated this run; **screen inventory = `src/make-import/src/app/routes.tsx` + screens/** + tech-spec.

